Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要穿过这里就是人类世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很高兴呢 月音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激动到大喊回来了 就像人类一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为月音在人类世界生活了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 对吧 月音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的无法忘怀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音 接住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不害怕人类世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一点也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪的学园更让人害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣里进了好多沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么一瞬间 我觉得月音说不定是人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你在说什么啊 胡梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这个了 开心地玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是难得的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接球 小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太小了 我没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受别人挑战的是淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球 月音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人类世界使用这个是不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做过头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边都是生的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比较喜欢吃生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海 真美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别待在那里了 来这边玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香 我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该道歉的是我 萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明知吸血鬼不能沾水的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情请参照第五话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去游泳吧 月音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧 胡梦她们在等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香在这里嘛 我也要留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来海边嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩得开心才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香不在的话 我开心不起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音 真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香 你刚刚想吸月音的血对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吸的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌…萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 月音味道很香的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿什么嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音要是倒在人类世界里的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我会照顾他的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我来照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是我来照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是元凶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（禁止入内）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的向日葵田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用来观光的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是这么漂亮的地方 为什么会没人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 竟然走到这种地方来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用这么着急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不知道那个传言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里大概就是那个持续发生失踪事件的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失踪事件？在这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让人发寒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地人都说是魔女在作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说因为这个山丘的开发计划惹怒了魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就引发了失踪事件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里被称为「魔女之丘」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说很久之前就有魔女住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在哪个网站看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个传说在这附近是很有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫的族人会绑架人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然盲目相信传言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然胡梦的头脑很简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌不可爱的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也讨厌满脑子H的梦魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 明明只是个小孩子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 突然干什么啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有个盆子掉下来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是问你这个事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那什么态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回海边去吧 老师还在等着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去后一定要把这事报告给馆主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 接下来就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师去找食物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物的话 这里有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错错错 既然来到海边了当然要吃新鲜的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类世界的鱼很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 你不会是因为这样才要来人类世界合宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 尾巴尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 馆主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会让那个小魔女成为我们的同伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得变得奇怪起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没办法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对小紫来说还是太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你搬这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香 我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被刀弄伤了手指就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫就在那边看着好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子只会碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都太把我当做小孩子了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以独当一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女之丘…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真的有魔女…有我的同伴在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摆出那么害怕的表情 小魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是瑠妃 是住在这个山丘上的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的同伴哦 小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天你不是来过这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起我就开始留意你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从没想过会在这里遇到其它魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫 我想和你做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没说不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是可以对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同是魔女 我们就好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伙又多一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然鱼还是人类世界的好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我只是想数一数啦 真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 小紫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类竟想破坏这么美丽的山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 我听说有什么开发计划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 所以要消灭人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会帮我的对吧 小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 我已经做好准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只按照馆主大人的计划去做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 我把你介绍给主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来魔女之丘生活吧 永远一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然不见了 真让人担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想继续破坏我们的山丘吗 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是魔草的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会袭击野兽和人类并吃掉的植物妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠妃小姐 你弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:18:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音不是想来破坏这个山丘的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫 退下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我通通吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫 别阻碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为月音是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不是魔女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 绝对不会让你加害他的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上没有比魔女的羁绊更强烈的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是存在的话 就由我来抹杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里失踪的人都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 我已经使不出力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是个小孩子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我已经不再是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日结果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次萌香都没有变身啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全都是小紫干的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点累而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 为什么要这样乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教训一会再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先带她回帐篷去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能和瑠妃小姐一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了别勉强了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女的自我治愈能力是很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口不对心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口不对心的是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫 好像已经没关系了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你们两个都没事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说去找她以后 也一直没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心你会不会是遇到什么事故了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假以来 终于能够两人独处了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月…月音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何我也要把小紫带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是馆主大人的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.35,0:22:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香 月音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…竟然把月音给…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.64,0:24:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为你们特别制作了刨冰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.78,0:24:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉凉的 冻得脑子一激灵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.57,0:24:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激灵~激灵~激灵~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.70,0:24:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是吃这个的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.93,0:24:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周会更糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.02,0:24:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 向日葵与吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.03,0:24:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你抱在怀里 亲~
